episodes.title: The Darkside of Dance: Shen yun lawsuit exposes the Falun gong cult with Amanda Yee
episodes.description:
Amanda Yee, journalist, editor, organiser and co-host of The China Report on @BreakThroughNews discusses the lawsuit against the anti-communist, anti-China dance company, Shen yun which reportedly ammassed over 250 million dollars in profit since its founding.
